snippet.title: Panchin is Frustrated: An idle game about creative block
snippet.description:
Play it here: https://forwardinstinct.itch.io/panchin-is-frustrated

Made for PIGSquad's Summer Slow Jams 2023 series, for the Idle jam in June 2023. Interact through dreams and twitch commands.
